不，阿德里安·布洛迪并没有因为他的牙买加印象而被禁止参加《周六夜现场》 https://www.nme.com/news/tv/no-adrien-brody-didnt-get-banned-from-snl-for-his-jamaican-impression-3826905?utm _source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=没有阿德里安布罗迪没有因为他的牙买加印象而被 snl 禁止Adam EnglandTue, 07 Jan 2025 20:04:32 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3826905 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾德里安·布罗迪" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我也从未被邀请回来”</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/no-adrien-brody-didnt-get-banned-from-snl-for-his-jamaican-impression-3826905">《不，阿德里安·布罗迪并没有因为他的牙买加印象而被禁止参加《SNL》》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾德里安·布罗迪" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-Golden-Globes-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>阿德里安·布罗迪 (Adrien Brody) 讨论了 20 多年前他因一部涉及牙买加口音的有争议短剧而被禁止参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/saturday-night-live"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>的说法。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/movies-2025-captain-america-avatar-led-zeppelin-3825912">2025 年上映的 20 部绝对不容错过的电影</a></strong></li></ul><p>出生于纽约市的布罗迪在 2003 年的亮相中，戴着辫子假发，用夸张的牙买加口音介绍了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sean-paul">肖恩·保罗</a>。保罗在加勒比岛国首府金斯敦出生并长大。</p><p>在 40 秒的介绍中，布罗迪偏离了滑雪道，一改通常的“女士们先生们，肖恩·保罗”，重复了一些典型的牙买加短语，提到了拉斯塔法里，还开玩笑说保罗的家人都被命名为不同的版本的“肖恩”。</p><p>此后的二十年里，布罗迪——本月晚些时候在英国上映的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-brutalist">《野兽派》</a></em>中的主演——再也没有出现在<em>《周六夜现场》</em>中，人们认为这一刻可能就是原因。但事实证明情况可能并非如此，布罗迪声称<em>《周六夜现场》</em>实际上为他提供了服装，并观看了彩排。 </p><figure id="attachment_3826913" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3826913" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="wp-image-3826913 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-The-Brutalist.jpg" alt="阿德里安·布洛迪在《野兽派》中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-The-Brutalist.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-The-Brutalist-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-The-Brutalist-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-The-Brutalist-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-The-Brutalist-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Adrien-Brody-The-Brutalist-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3826913" class="wp-caption-text">阿德里安·布洛迪在《野兽派》中。图片来源：环球影业</figcaption></figure><p>他形容制片人对他对这部剧的丰富想法感到“惊叹不已”，包括印象，他告诉<a href="https://www.vulture.com/article/the-brutalist-movie-adrien-brody-actor-oscar-career-legacy.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Vulture</em></a> ：“我认为洛恩（迈克尔斯，<em>周六夜现场的</em>创作者）对我的修饰不满意，但他们允许我，”他说。 “奇怪的是，我认为这是一个安全的空间。”</p><p>当被问及他现在是否被禁止时，他说据他所知，但补充了一个警告：“我也从未被邀请回来，所以我不知道该告诉你什么。”</p><p>布罗迪短剧的片段几乎已从公众视野中删除，并且无法在<em>SNL</em>的任何官方频道上观看。</p><p>与此同时，周日（1 月 5 日），布罗迪<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/golden-globes-2025-see-the-full-list-of-winners-3826190">凭借在<em>《野兽派》</em>中的表演赢得了金球奖</a>——他在剧中饰演出生于匈牙利、移居美国的拉斯洛·托特 (László Tóth)。</p><p>他在获奖感言中情绪激动，向他“美丽而神奇”的女友致敬，并告诉她，“如果没有你，我就不会站在你面前。”</p><p>他补充道：“这个故事中人物的旅程确实让人想起我母亲和我祖先逃离战争恐怖来到这个伟大国家的旅程，你知道，我非常感谢我的母亲和祖父母的牺牲。 ” </p><p><iframe title="阿德里安·布洛迪 (Adrien Brody) 荣获剧情类最佳男演员奖第 82 届金球奖" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/a5EhthtF44Y?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>广受影评人好评的<em>《野兽派</em>》将于 1 月 24 日在英国上映。影片由菲丽希缇·琼斯、盖·皮尔斯、乔·阿尔文、拉菲·卡西迪和布罗迪等明星主演。</p><p> <em>NME</em>的詹姆斯·莫特拉姆 (James Mottram) 将其<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/movies-2025-captain-america-avatar-led-zeppelin-3825912">列入 2025 年不容错过的电影清单</a>，并将其描述为“艺术天堂”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/no-adrien-brody-didnt-get-banned-from-snl-for-his-jamaican-impression-3826905">不，阿德里安·布罗迪并没有因为他的牙买加印象而被禁止参加《SNL》，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
比利·科根、约翰·5、罗尼·拉德克出席玛丽莲·曼森的生日派对https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-john-5-ronnie-radke-attend-marilyn-mansons-birthday-party-3826866?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=billy-corgan-john- 5-罗尼·拉德克参加玛丽莲·曼森的生日派对Anagricel DuranTue, 07 Jan 2025 19:27:10 +0000 Music NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3826866 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛丽莲·曼森、比利·考根和罗尼·拉德克。图片来源：Medios y Media、Kevin Winter 和 Javier Bragado，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Smashing Pumpkins 的 James Iha 和 Richard Patrick 也出席了活动</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billy-corgan-john-5-ronnie-radke-attend-marilyn-mansons-birthday-party-3826866">比利·科根、约翰·5、罗尼·拉德克参加玛丽莲·曼森生日派对的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛丽莲·曼森、比利·考根和罗尼·拉德克。图片来源：Medios y Media、Kevin Winter 和 Javier Bragado，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Marylin-Manson-Billy-Corgan-and-Ronnie-Radke.-Credit-Medios-y-Media-Kevin-Winter-and-Javier-Bragado-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Billy-Corgan">Billy Corgan</a> 、James Iha、 <a href="/artists/Falling-in-Reverse">Falling in Reverse</a>的 Ronnie Radke 等人都出席了<a href="/artists/Marilyn-Manson">玛丽莲·曼森</a>的生日派对。</p><p>这位备受争议的音乐家于 1 月 5 日庆祝了自己的 56 岁生日，在看似酒吧或餐厅的地方举办了一场私密派对。曼森的朋友之一凡妮莎·亚历山德拉 (Vanessa Alexandra) 以及玛丽莲·曼森 (Marylin Manson) 粉丝帐户 @marilynmanson.gallery 在 Instagram 上分享了当晚的各种照片和视频片段。</p><p>在一段视频中，一群受邀嘉宾花了一点时间向这位音乐家唱“生日快乐”。他还花时间感谢大家的到来，并表示一个月后他将戒酒四年。</p><p>科根和他的<a href="/artists/Smashing-Pumpkins">Smashing Pumpkins</a>乐队成员 Iha 出现在派对上可能会让人感到惊讶。曼森和柯根曾一度陷入长期不和，因为《美丽人民》的歌手告诉这位《1979》的热门制作人他很像查理·布朗。然而，2014年，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/smashing-pumpkins-55-1213976">曼森加入粉碎南瓜乐队在伦敦登台演出后，两人似乎已经和好。</a></p><p>其他出席者包括<a href="/artists/Motley-Crüe">Motley Crüe</a>吉他手 John 5、美国摄影师 Joseph Cultice（他执导了曼森纪录片《 <em>Dead to the World》</em>和该歌手的《索多玛苹果》音乐录影带，也是曼森《机械动物》专辑艺术作品的摄影师）——理查德·帕特里克 (Richard Patrick)（滤镜、 <a href="/artists/Nine-inch-Nails">《九寸钉》</a> ) 导演 Bill Yukich、音乐家 Wednesday 13 等。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DEfLBJkM2Yz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.5